parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel System Failure - Plastic Fuel Line Quick Disconnect Fitting
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the plastic fuel line quick disconnect fitting can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires, explosions, and accidents, potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: fuel dripping onto the engine or garage floor
and difficulty accessing the engine for maintenance.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel System Failure - Fuel Pump and Fuel Lines
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump and fuel lines can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires, explosions, and accidents, potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: fuel dripping onto the engine or garage floor
and difficulty accessing the engine for maintenance.
